title: [Icemule Trace, Exterior]
description: A sheer cliff of ice blocks the ice trail.  A crevice opens in the wall, likely leading into and perhaps under the glacier.  The sparkle of the sun on the ice is nearly blinding, making your eyes squint and water.
A sheer cliff of ice blocks the ice trail.  A crevice opens in the wall, likely leading into and perhaps under the glacier.  Moonlight sparkles on the ice illuminating the area.
